structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
HEALTH AND WELFARE IN CITIES OF THE FIRST CLASS AND IN COUNTIES CONTAINING SUCH CITIES

law.catch_line: Suspension of applicable provisions of KRS Chapter 201.
law.text: The provisions of Kentucky Revised Statutes, Chapter 201, relating to the establishment of a board for city and county children's home, shall be suspended upon the transfer of control of the functions and property of said board as provided in KRS 98.330, during the term of such agreement.
law.history: Created 1956 (1st Extra. Sess.) Ky. Acts ch. 3, sec. 10, effective June 6, 1956.
